  "original_title": "\u0db4\u0dcf\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dbd\u0dd2\u0db8\u0dda\u0db1\u0dca\u0dad\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0dda \u0da1\u0db1\u0dca\u0daf\u0dba\u0dad\u0dca \u0da2\u0db1\u0dad\u0dcf \u0db8\u0dad\u0dba\u0dad\u0dca \u0d85\u0dad\u0dbb \u0d86\u0dbd\u0ddd\u0d9a \u0dc0\u0dbb\u0dca\u0dc2 \u0d9c\u0dab\u0db1\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0d9a \u0db4\u0dbb\u0dad\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "There is a gap of many light years between the vote of the Parliament and the opinion of the people",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The education secretary of Vanguard Socialist Party Mr. Pubudu Jayagoda said this afternoon (20) that there is a gap of many light years between the percentage of votes in the parliament and the opinion of the people outside and that the people's power of the country was used to remove the Gotabhaya Rajapaksa president who had 69 lakh votes and two-thirds power.",
        "Mr. Pubudu Jayagoda said that it was clearly demonstrated in the election of the President that the opinion of the people was not represented by the 225 members of the Parliament and also mentioned that the people's representatives in the Parliament have belittled the opinion, political aspirations, questions and grievances of over 200 lakh people outside the Parliament.",
        "Mr. Jayagoda said that since the people of the country did not have confidence in the Parliament for a long time, they had to go to the Araliya Ganga Mandiara to solve the problems and the slogans of 'power in the hands of the people' have been confirmed by the Parliament today.",
        "The Education Secretary of Vanguard Socialist Party Mr. Pubudu Jayagoda said this at a special press conference held today in Colombo to comment on the presidential appointment vote held in Parliament."
      ],
